{
  "stem": "2723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one of the women who-- it was strange, because the camp looked completely deserted but for those who lay on the ground, just discharging feces all the time, uncontrollably.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I look at the pictures of [INAUDIBLE], so I realize that really, the action is exactly-- bodies are the same when they're completely debilitated.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And out of nowhere, able-bodied people surfaced.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it transpired that a number of women who actually were office-bearers in Ravensbruck, working for the Germans, chose not to leave the camp, for whatever their reasons.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't care at that stage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started barking orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And maybe that brought a kind of bearable reality into our situation again, because we followed those orders.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were women like us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they were more able-bodied, mostly Czech, non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, well, we may as well die in dignity.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And let's occupy the German barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know what I occupied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I was in a-- in a kind of a bunk bed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't make the highest bunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I got to the middle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the middle was window height.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I then recall nothing, only the fact that I woke up, and it was dark, and I was still alive, and there was no big bang.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I could hear the sounds of a motorbike.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was sure I was hallucinating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the motorbike was coming closer and closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then I heard a voice cooing or making noise, noises as if waiting for responses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And none came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I understood Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had learned it in camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I heard a Russian voice say, hm, they promised us girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there are no bloody girls here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where are the girls?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
